  "original_title": "One-Day Passport Service in three more districts",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "One-Day Passport Service in three more districts",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Department of Immigration and Emigration says that the one-day passport issuance service will be implemented in three more districts from Monday (4).",
        "Accordingly, the one-day service will be implemented in Vavuniya, Matara, and Kandy districts.",
        "At present, the one-day service is operational only at the head office of the Department of Immigration and Emigration in Colombo.",
        "Controller General Sarath Rupasiri said that after making an appointment, one-day passport services can be obtained from Vavuniya, Matara, and Kandy district offices.",
        "He mentioned that 3,000 people visit Colombo daily to get passports through the one-day service.",
        "Yupun becomes first South Asian to finish 100m below 10 seconds & win"
      ],
